programme.desc: Ruslan and Nunik, a married couple who work as scrap metal thieves, found various ways to make a profit by ordering their men to steal iron.

programme.title: Sayap Pelindung Cintaku
programme.desc: Karena baru putus dengan Darin, Alena sangat sedih dan kini ia lebih sering menyendiri. Jadinya Pipi yang pusing, mengajak adik kesayangannya liburan ke pantai. Setiba di pantai, Alena bertemu Petra pemuda yang menolongnya sewaktu tersesat.

programme.title: Sayap Pelindung Cintaku
programme.desc: Because she just broke up with Darin, Alena is very sad and now she is often alone. So, Pipi, who is dizzy, takes her beloved sister on holiday to the beach. Upon arrival, Alena meets Petra, a young man who helped her when she was lost.

programme.title: Ramalan Cinta Tukang Siomay
programme.desc: Ramalan cinta dari peramal itu sudah biasa, tapi bagaimana kalau ramalan dari tukang siomay? Apakah itu bisa jadi kenyataan?

programme.title: Ramalan Cinta Tukang Siomay
programme.desc: Love predictions from fortune tellers are common, but what about the predictions from dumpling seller? Coult it become true?

programme.title: Pacar 30 Hari
programme.desc: Ketika menghadiri reuni SMA, Olive bertemu dengan Bayu, cowok yang dulu naksir dirinya. Olive terpesona melihat penampilan Bayu sekarang yang kini sudah sangat berubah dibanding yang dulu. Bayu pun punya usaha dibidang fashion.

programme.title: Pacar 30 Hari
programme.desc: While attending a high school reunion, Olive meets Bayu, a boy who used to have a crush on her. Olive was fascinated by Bayu's current appearance, which changed greatly compared to before. Bayu also has a business in fashion.

programme.title: Kepentok Cinta Long Distance
programme.desc: Niko dipindah ke tempat kantor yang baru dari tempat kerja sebelumnya, sehingga dia harus LDR dengan pacarnya. Tak disangka, ia bertemu dengan mantannya, Dena, cewek nyebelin yang bekerja di kantor yang sama dengan Niko.

programme.title: Kepentok Cinta Long Distance
programme.desc: Niko moved to another branch, therefore he was forced to keep his relationship with his girlfriend long-distanced. Soon after, he unexpectedly met his ex, Dena, the annoying girl who turned out worked in the same office as him.

programme.title: Jadi Kera Karena Ingin Kaya
programme.desc: Shanti anak penjual sayur sok kaya. Ia banyak berhutang ke renternir untuk berfoya-foya hingga tega menjadikan sertifikat rumah ibunya sebagai jaminan. Ingin cepat kaya, Shanti melakukan ritual dan melakukan perjanjian dengan siluman kera.

programme.title: Jadi Kera Karena Ingin Kaya
programme.desc: Shanti is a rich vegetable seller. She owes a lot to moneylenders for such extravagance that she use her mother's house certificate as warranty. Wanting to get rich quickly, Shanti performs rituals and makes a pact with the monkey demon.

programme.title: Azab Perebut Harta Warisan
programme.desc: Tiap perbuatan ada ganjarannya. Kali ini, saksikan kisah seseorang yang merebut harta warisan mendapatkan hukumannya.

programme.title: Azab Perebut Harta Warisan
programme.desc: Every deed has its consequences. This time, watch the story of how someone gets punishment from taking over inheritance unfairly.

programme.title: Factory Cinta
programme.desc: Karin melaksanakan tugas KKN di sebuah desa terpencil selama dua minggu. Merasa bosan, dia dan sahabatnya, Dinda, pergi ke kota untuk berbelanja tapi justru kemalingan dan tersesat. Lalu, Aman, pemuda desa yang ganteng datang menyelamatkannya.

programme.title: Factory Cinta
programme.desc: Karin carries out Community Service assignments in a remote village for two weeks. Be bored, she and her best friend, Dinda, go to town to shop but she's getting stolen and lost. Then, Aman, a handsome village youth, comes to save her.

programme.title: My Secret Admirer
programme.desc: Rian tinggal bersebelahan dengan Syerly dan kuliah di kampus yang sama. Mereka kerap bertengkar dan saling jahil.Celine, sahabat Syerly menyarankannya jadian sama Rian,namun Syerly bertekad lebih baik jomblo dari pada dengan Rian si cowok jahil.

programme.title: My Secret Admirer
programme.desc: Rian lives next door to Syerly and studies at the same campus. They often quarrel and misbehave with each other. Celine, Syerly's best friend, suggests Syerly to be with Rian, but Syerly is determined that it's better to be single than to be with Rian, the naughty boy.

programme.title: From Lucky With Love
programme.desc: Hati Lucky hancur karena Aryo,kekasihya selingkuh.Ketika di jalan tanpa sengaja Rayhan menemukan sobekan photo.Rayhan penasaran siapa wanita yang ada di photo itu. Tiba-tiba Rayhan menabrak Lucky di jalan.Apakah Lucky akan menemukan sosok pengganti Aryo?

programme.title: From Lucky With Love
programme.desc: Lucky's heart was broken because Aryo, his lover cheated on him. While on the road Rayhan accidentally found a torn photo. Rayhan was curious who the woman in the photo was. Rayhan suddenly bumps into Lucky on the road. Will Lucky find a replacement for Aryo?

programme.title: Cinta Km 07
programme.desc: Dinda, tukang tambal ban cantik, membuat para pelanggan rela antre agar kendaraannya bisa ditambal oleh Dinda. Mobil Rangga mogok dan dia meminta bantuan Dinda, diam-diam Rangga jatuh hati dengan Dinda.

programme.title: Cinta Km 07
programme.desc: Dinda, a beautiful mechanic, can easily attract more costumers. A guy named Rangga got his car broken and ask for Dinda's help to fix it. What Dinda doesn't know is he starts to catch feelings for her.
